<p>Hurricane Melissa rapidly intensified into a major Category 4 storm with maximum sustained winds reported near 140 mph, and meteorologists say it is likely to make landfall in Jamaica early next week, threatening catastrophic flooding and landslides across parts of the northern Caribbean . Forecasts show the system may pass near the Dominican Republic before reaching Jamaica and could bring extreme rainfall—over 30 inches in some locations—particularly endangering Haiti and Jamaica&#x27;s interior river basins and slopes . Agencies and local authorities have issued hurricane warnings and urged residents to seek shelter immediately as emergency preparations continue .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/LqnMMoZAnTI_EpDaUPJchbDBnoavsaQ76RaS0Qy3PpDnoFlXoRrA4Cd6xbNp8Kxp0qCmeUfVBntNsA9rxyLk5KZY9yqOQpyecqIKayY7vNKNs9KOFRzYtJF3lb5LidN2Ok8MrvfjScehQrqGIDgvYxAy_6tGsfIlCgqODoAJLw' alt='Satellite or news image associated with reports of Hurricane Melissa strengthening in the Caribbean' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Rapid intensification: Meteorologists documented Melissa&#x27;s fast escalation from a tropical system into a major hurricane over a short period, a pattern that complicates forecasts and shortens preparation time .</li><li>Local preparations: Kingston&#x27;s waterfront was largely emptied and some neighborhoods were still racing to secure property and move people to safer locations as the first bands of rain arrived .</li><li>Regional track: Forecast models show Melissa tracking past or near the Dominican Republic before reaching Jamaica, with forecasters warning Cuba could also see impacts depending on the storm&#x27;s evolution .</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>National Hurricane Center / meteorologists: Forecasters warned that Melissa could produce catastrophic flash flooding and dangerous landslides across parts of Jamaica, Haiti and the Dominican Republic and urged immediate protective action. (<a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/melissa-maps-forecast-atlantic-ocean/'>CBS News</a>)</li><li>Local Jamaican authorities and responders: Officials and emergency crews in Kingston encouraged residents to shelter and take urgent steps to secure property as the storm&#x27;s first bands reached the island. (<a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/video/jamaica-braces-hurricane-melissa-after-passes-dominican-republic/'>CBS News (video report)</a>)</li><li>Haitian authorities / local reports: Authorities reported fatalities linked to Melissa&#x27;s impacts in Haiti and highlighted the acute risk from heavy rain in vulnerable, flood-prone areas. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/ckgkqvxkzx0o'>BBC News</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/melissa-gathers-strength-before-catastrophic-landfall-in-jamaica/a-74498637'>Melissa gathers strength before &#x27;catastrophic&#x27; landfall in Jamaica</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/comments/1ogb0b0/hurricane_melissa_rapidly_intensifying_forecast/'>Hurricane Melissa rapidly intensifying, forecast to become a rare Category 5</a> - reddit.com</li><li><a href='https://www.boston.com/weather/weather/2025/10/26/hurricane-melissa-jamaica/'>Melissa strengthens into a Category 4 hurricane, threatening catastrophic flooding in Jamaica, Haiti</a> - boston.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/melissa-maps-forecast-atlantic-ocean/'>Hurricane Melissa strengthens into a powerful Category 4 storm</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/news-wrap-rapidly-intensifying-melissa-becomes-a-hurricane-in-the-caribbean'>News Wrap: Rapidly intensifying Melissa becomes a hurricane in the Caribbean</a> - pbs.org</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/melissa-strengthens-category-3-hurricane-threating-catastrophic-flooding-126872056'>Melissa strengthens into a Category 3 hurricane, threating catastrophic flooding in Jamaica, Haiti</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='ht